    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal wear and tear, the interior remains clean and comfortable. All major systems are functioning as they should, offering a solid balance of performance and value.",
